This paper deals with the design of a robust transceiver for a multi-user multi-cell MIMO interference network. The paper focuses on interference alignment and channel estimation error, which are both topics related to information theory (cs.IT). The paper also deals with wireless communication networks (cs.NI) and signal processing (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper deals with multi-user and multi-cell networks (cs.MM) and optimization (cs.LG).
